<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br><font face="Arial, sans-serif">I’m still struggling to reach you since you provided your details via our Facebook form.</font><br><br></p><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">To provide the best quote for you I need to understand your business and the level of cover you might require.<b>&nbsp;Is there a good time for me to give you a call?</b></font><br><b style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></b><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Alternatively, you can contact me on&nbsp;</font><b style="font-size: 12pt;">01242 808 740</b><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">. Our office is open between the hours of 8:00am-5:30pm, Monday-Friday.&nbsp;</font><br><br><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">You can also get a quote online via our website&nbsp;</font><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><a href="http://www.kingsbridge.co.uk/">www.kingsbridge.co.uk</a></span></font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">.</font><br><br><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;">I look forward to hearing from you soon.&nbsp;</font><br><br><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: white;">Kind regards,</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">{!User.FirstName}</font><br><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Sales Team</font><br><br><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk</font><br><font style="font-size: 12pt;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt;">01242 808740</font></div>]]></td>
</tr>
